data.description: Step into this awesome updated home! It's got three bedrooms and the main floor is totally fresh with new floors, cool paint, and fancy countertops. Plus, there's a whole upper level for chilling out or having fun. And guess what? There's even a huge basement waiting for you to turn it into whatever you want! Outside, there's a bunch of decks, a porch, and even a storage spot. All of this sits on a big piece of land, making it the perfect place to call home!
